eeditor.description:
# TwoSides COUNTRY RECOMMENDATIONS
> **1. Highly recommended:**
> 1) German Empire - the path to fascism could turn all of Europe upside down.
> 2) Soviet Union - maintains its own order in Eastern Europe, but internal party strife is seriously hindering this. I strongly advise against changing ideology.
> 3) American Confederates - if you really want to, you can become the strongest country in the world, despite not being a major power.
>
> **2. Recommended:**
> 1) Italy - Germany's ally, trying to restore the Roman Empire.
> 2) Sweden - also an ally, building Scandinavia.
> 3) Japan - could put up a serious fight.
> 
> **3. Consider:**
> 1) Great Britain - lots of discontent and the possibility of civil war, but at least it's one of the world's leading powers. 
> 2) France - according to canon, it's heading towards communism, and the Raccoon loves that, so it's a good country. (WATCH PARIS!!!)
> 3) Turkey - not the same Ottoman Empire many people know, but still not degraded, nothing special.
> 
> **4. I like: **
> 1) Yugoslavia - there's plenty of time to prepare before Italy attacks, and there's also a good opportunity for communism to emerge.
